  "author": "XO_OX",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "XVC ADVANCED 4: Hat choke active + kick_to_snare_filter at 1.0 with global_amount 0.95. The kick physically compresses the snare's tonal brightness — a strong kick hit pushes snare tone to maximum, mimicking sidechain compression as timbral coupling. Not volume ducking: the snare filter opens on kick, closes between kicks. The kit breathes through brightness rather than amplitude.",
